name: Jellyseerr Discovery
description: Discover actor filmography and studio catalogs via Jellyseerr/TMDb
overview: Browse complete filmographies for actors and catalogs for studios/networks. See what content is available, requested, or can be requested through Jellyseerr. Perfect for discovering new content to add to your library.
